  /*
    <h1>Wiki Archive</h1>
  
  {{# if this.model.export_available}}
  
  <p>Ares can create a downloadable archive of the game's scenes, characters, and wiki pages. You can keep this for your reference even after a game closes and the web portal is no longer available.</p>
  
  <p><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/game/wiki_export.zip">Download Archive</a></p>
  
  <p>To use the archive, just unzip it and drag and drop the <code>index.html</code> file into your web browser of choice. See <a href="/help/wiki_archive">Wiki Archive Help</a> for more information.</p>
  
  <div class="alert alert-info">
  Archive last updated on {{this.model.last_exported}}.
  {{#if this.model.auto_export}}
  This archive will be updated daily.
  {{else}}
  This archive is not updated automatically; ask the game admin if you would like a newer copy.
  {{/if}}
  </div>
  
  {{else}}
  
  The game admin have not enabled a wiki archive. Contact them for details.
  
  {{/if}}
  */
